-- Colombia's central bank to halt dollar purchases
-- By Carlos Vargas
-- Fri Dec 19, 2014 01:28PM EST
-- None



BOGOTA, Dec 19 (Reuters) - Colombia's central bank monetary policy board will allow its dollar buying programme to expire this month, director Jose Dario Uribe said on Friday, and it did not adopt other measures to lessen recent volatility in the peso exchange rate.   (Reporting by Carlos Vargas; Writing by Peter Murphy)  ((Peter.Murphy@thomsonreuters.com; +57 1 634 4133; Reuters Messaging: peter.murphy.thomsonreuters.com@reuters.net))  Keywords: COLOMBIA FOREX/

